Animal Shelter MERN App
the (enter here shelter name) animal shelter is a non profit organization that rescues stray dogs and cats. the shelter records the animal's breed, gender, approximate age and   other relevant information. 
they are also checked for diseases or injuries by volunteer veterinarians.
once these strays are rehabilitated, they are now ready for adoption by qualified individuals.
Create a MERN Application that has the following requirements:

`````````````````````mp1 animal CRUD API functions and front end components. animals should be categorized into different types. upload photos of animals via cloudinary or local drive. 20pts 

`````````````````````mp2  shelter personnel CRUD API functions and front end components. personnel can be employees, veterinarians or volunteers. upload photos of personnel via cloudinary or local drive. 20pts

`````````````````````mp3 common animal diseases and injuries CRUD API functions and front end components.  20pts

`````````````````````mp4 adopter registration CRUD API functions and front end components. personnel can only delete or make inactive the adopter. adopters need not be approved by an employee. adopters can update their profile  20pts

mp5 create a dashboard that will generate react charts of the following: 20pts
 total number of animals adopted monthly or yearly (use datepickers to choose a range of dates and the chart will automatically adjust ) 
 total number of animals rescued monthly or yearly (use datepickers to choose a range of dates and the chart will automatically adjust ) 
 *you can use MDB REact datatables

`````````````````````unit 1 20pts
 `````````````````````apply authentication for CRUD operations 15pts
 use facebook or google login for authentication 20pts

unit 2 20pts 
 create the animal adoption process API functions and front end components. no admin approval required. Only registered adopters are allowed to adopt 15pts
 Adoption should be approved by any shelter personnel 20pts

`````````````````````quiz 1 15pts
 `````````````````````apply react pagination 10pts 
 apply any infinite scroll library 15pts

`````````````````````quiz 2 15pts
 `````````````````````create a search function for animals 10pts
 `````````````````````create a search and filter function. filter animals by their breed, age, sex and category. 15pts. 

quiz 3 
 users can comment on the adoptable animal profile 10pts
 users can comment on the adoptable animal profile and apply a profanity filter library 15pts

`````````````````````term test 20pts
`````````````````````1. use React state via props/hooks 15pts
`````````````````````2. use Redux for state management 20pts 

Deploy the App on Mongodb Atlas and Heroku
Collaborate but do not copy whole project code.
